Most of the active ingredients in the formula are derived from natural extracts such as Mulberry, Licorice and Bearberry plants. Civant Skin Care puts your safety above anything else. Our products contain absolutely no hydroquinone, mercury, steroids or other harmful bleaching substances.Your skin color comes from a natural pigment called melanin. Melanin pigment is synthesized in specialized cytoplasmic organelles called melanosomes. Within the melanosome, the enzymatic conversion of the amino acid tyrosine to melanin is catalyzed by the enzyme tyrosinase. The melanosomes in darker portions of the skin are more active than those found in normal areas of the body. Ideally, it is best to target this process in multiple ways by dealing with not only the melanosomes, but also the enzyme tyrosinase.In order to naturally fade dark skin spots and obtain an even complexion, you must dedicate time and patience to the process. When combined with exfoliation agents, Meladerm® often provides initial results within 2 weeks of use, however, full results generally take 2-3 months and vary based on the individual's specific skin physiology and condition.What is Meladerm used for?Meladerm® is generally used to reduce the appearance of hyperpigmented skin on the body or face. Many of our customers use the product to achieve a uniform skin tone by reducing the appearance of uneven areas and dark spots. Meladerm® can be used on the face and body for specific areas such as:•Hyperpigmentation / Dark discolorations•Age / Liver spots / Sun spots•Freckles•Tans / Sun damage•Melasma / Chloasma•Acne marks•Old scars•Birthmarks•Dark elbows, knees, underarms, knuckles•Uneven skin tones

Description: Alternative Anti-AgingProducts with neem oil offer an alternative to synthetic anti-aging products, as the carotenoid content of neem lends it potentially protective qualities; according to a 2009 study published in “Toxicology and Industrial Health,” beta-carotene shields the skin against oxidative stress and ultraviolet radiation, helping reduce the signs of skin aging. Neem oil also contains vitamin C, a natural part of the skin's dermis and epidermis that features antioxidant properties and encourages collagen production. Like cartenoids, vitamin C helps prevent photodamage to the skin. Additionally, the fatty acids of neem oil serve as a moisturizer.Antiseptics for AcneNeem oil features antiseptic properties, which may help those suffering from acne. The plant contains quercetin, an antibacterial and anti-inflammatory flavonoid. Antibacterial agents help reduce acne in some cases, as pimples form due to the occurrence of bacteria in clogged follicles, which contributes to the creation of inflamed red pustules. Quercetin also serves as an antioxidant, which helps reduce membrane-damaging free radicals.Redness ReductionJust as quercetin may help reduce redness, neem oil features other anti-inflammatory components. Neem tree seeds, which produce neem oil, contain 28 liminoids -- chiefly nimbin and its derivatives. As reported by a 2009 study in the “Journal of Oleo Science,” these liminoids exhibit marked anti-inflammatory properties with almost no toxicity. Anti-inflammatory agents such as these can ease the appearance of redness on the skin.

Title: NOVA BIOS TULSI POWDER(200 g)
Description: Holy basil, also known as Tulsi in India, is a wonderful Ayurvedic product. It’s medicinal, beauty and other uses are widely known. Tulsi has so many beauty benefits like it lightens the skin tone, soothes the acne prone sensitive skin and even helps eliminating pimples/acne. There are some amazing benefits that Tulsi can give us. Tulsi packs also remove the pimple marks from face.1. Tulsi face pack of Nova Bios used for skin brightening as mentioned A. Take 1g Nova Bios Tulsi Powder and half a teaspoonful of milk powder. Mix with some water and add the milk powder to form a paste of medium consistency. Apply this paste on the face and let it dry for 20 minutes. Rinse the face with plain water. This Tulsi face pack is excellent for brightening the skin. It adds an instant glow on the skin and skin feels instantly brightened due to the lactic acid and Tulsi in it. This can be done 2 times a week and it’s good for all skin types including the sensitive skin as well.2. Tulsi face pack for acne prone skinYou will need 1g Nova Bios Tulsi Powder and Nova Bios Neem Leaf Powder and half a teaspoonful of sandalwood powder. Grind all the three ingredients with some rose water. Once you get the paste, apply it on the cleansed face and wash off after 20 minutes. This Tulsi and neem face pack is wonderful for acne prone skin and both the ingredients are powerful anti-inflammatory and anti bacterial. Sandal wood further soothes the skin. You can use this 2 times a week.3. Tulsi face pack for Dry skinDry skin can be difficult to tackle especially during winters then you can try this Tulsi face pack to combat the dryness and get the instant glow. Take some Nova Bios tulsi Powder, add some yoghurt and mix it well. Apply it on the face and keep for 15-20 minutes. This will quickly make the skin supple and nourished.4. Multani Mitti and Tulsi face pack for Oily skinWhile dry skin is hard to tackle, same is the case with oily skin as it is more likely to get pimples and break outs. This Multani Mitti face pack with powdered Tulsi leaves will be excellent to keep the skin oil free and clear. Take a teaspoonful of multani mitti (Fuller’s earth) and mix it with some tulsi leaves Powder. You can dilute the paste with some rose water or just the plain water. This is really easy to prepare. You will have to keep it for 20 minutes and it can be tried 2 times a week for oily skin to keep the skin problems away.5. Tulsi face pack for fading marks and pimplesTulsi face pack that would be every effective in removing the marks and scars left by the breaks outs. You will need 10-12 Tulsi leaves and tomato pulp. Mix tomato pulp with powdered leaves and apply this on your face for 15 minutes and rinse off with cold water.Gradually the marks and pimples will fade revealing a clear skin that glows. Tulsi is a wonderful product that will give you clear bright skin. So, try these face packs consistently and let the change in your skin texture.Tulsi is used as mouth wash for reducing tooth ache. Its powdered leaves, can be used for brushing teeth. It can also be mixed with mustered oil to make a paste and used as toothpaste. This is very good for maintaining dental health, counteracting bad breath and for massaging the gums. It is also useful in pyorrhea and other teeth disorders.
